HEADWORD: Monostrophic
<hw>Mon`o*stroph"ic</hw> <pr>(m⟦ocr⟧n`⟦osl⟧*str⟦ocr⟧f"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>monostrofiko`s</grk>; <grk>mo`nos</grk>
